body:json {
  {}
}

docs {
  v1.17.1 — pycupra-style fallback URL for aux-heating stop.

  Used by SeatCupraClient.command_stop_aux_heating() as the
  legacy/fallback path when the Bruno-verified primary path
  ``/v1/vehicles/{vin}/auxiliary-heating/stop`` (seq 32) returns 404.

  No SecToken on stop (Bruno seq 30 confirmed).
}
